Cook rice according to package instructions. Heat large skillet with cooking spray over medium high heat and then add chicken. Cook chicken 3-5 minutes or until brown and partially cooked. Add broccoli, mushrooms, onion and garlic cook 4-5 minutes or until vegetables are tender yet still crisp. Stir in rice, mustard, honey, vinegar, tarragon, salt and pepper. Cook 2-3 minutes or until well-blended.